overview: All Elite Wrestling's second annual November brawl has Matt Hardy taking on Sammy Guevara in an Elite Deletion Match, the Finals of the World Championship Eliminator Tournament, Jon Moxley defending his AEW World Championship in an "I Quit" Match against Eddie Kingston, and for the first time ever, one of the most anticipated matches in years has FTR facing off against the Young Bucks for the AEW Tag Team Championships.
title: AEW Full Gear
